{"tid":1071971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細個會覺得呢兩首大時大節先播嘅歌好老土","createTime":"2019-03-21T17:01:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T06:29:11.000Z","uid":208722,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a96b766d42277051a0863b6ac450ce541dc03847","tid":1071971,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eGwr7AK3Lnk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeGwr7AK3Lnk&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3MF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=3ee5e77f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eGwr7AK3Lnk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7sTMpb424Dw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7sTMpb424Dw&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3MF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=04f03224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7sTMpb424Dw</a><br />\n但而家發現，原來人大咗，過農曆新年，一家人坐埋一檯聽呢兩首歌食飯，係咁難能可貴&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n回想返，今年農曆新年又一樣冇聽過呢首歌，冇好好食個飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知重有幾多年光陰可以咁樣再齊人食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2e398240563f307dcdf79e7340cf7301ff1e742","tid":1071971,"uid":179979,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T17:06:54.000Z","msg":"好撚認同"},{"pid":"36252a